data.description: This charming ''old-Florida'' home presents an outstanding opportunity close to everything West Palm Beach has to offer. Located on a quiet street with a private and fully-fenced backyard with storage shed, mature landscaping, wide driveway and lovely curb-appeal.  Features of this light, bright and cheery home include 2 bedrooms, 1 bath, a small office nook, a spacious kitchen and partial hurricane impact windows.
